summary: Comprehensive frontend testing of Czech barber landing page completed. All core features and requirements tested successfully after retro teal/warm-dark visual redesign.

Hero CTA buttons functional (Objednat se, Služby & Ceník)
Navbar contains all required links (O nás, Služby, Galerie, Recenze, Kontakt) plus Zavolat CTA
Contact bar shows phone 737 553 735, address Skácelova, hours Po-Pá 14:00-20:00
Awards section displays Orlové Krásy with 5 award badges (2024-2026)
Services section contains 6 services with Czech currency (Kč) pricing
Reviews section shows 5.0 rating, Google badge, and 6 review cards
Contact section has address, phone, Instagram/Facebook links, Google Maps
Footer contains navigation links and social media icons
Google reviews links open in new tab to Google Maps
Mobile responsive design with functional hamburger menu
Retro teal/warm-dark visual styling applied correctly
